00:07:18.680 --> 00:07:21.890
Some of those we can
damp with oscillators.

00:07:21.890 --> 00:07:24.700
So we measure the oscillations.

00:07:24.700 --> 00:07:27.170
We have a very fast
feedback system.

00:07:27.170 --> 00:07:30.570
And then some kind of dampening
system tuned to that in order

00:07:30.570 --> 00:07:33.050
to damp it back down again.

00:07:33.050 --> 00:07:36.610
The ones in the main beam
with that spread of tunes

00:07:36.610 --> 00:07:39.110
that I was talking about,
unfortunately if you damp one,

00:07:39.110 --> 00:07:40.240
you'll drive another.

00:07:40.240 --> 00:07:43.190
So that makes it
slightly more difficult.

00:07:43.190 --> 00:07:47.610
